    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-08-27T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-08-27T00:00:00-05:00" n="112" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d112">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Denby</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Olney</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Peking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-08-27">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 27,
                                1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Consul had started Kutien under ray orders, with the consent of Chinese
                            Government and with escort furnished by them, before your cipher
                            telegram 12 was received, taking naval officer with him. Consul reports
                            the examination proceeding smoothly. Officials actively cooperating.
                            Many convictions secured.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Denby</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
